SSHFling Debian Source Package Draft
====================================

This directory is a packaging draft for Debian and Ubuntu review work. It is
not an upload-ready official archive package while the upstream LICENSE remains
proprietary, paid-use, and redistribution-restricted.

Before upload, resolve the legal gate recorded in
docs/official-distro-readiness.md, replace placeholder maintainer metadata, and
run the normal distro validation path:

* dpkg-buildpackage
* lintian
* autopkgtest
* WNPP/ITP and sponsor review for Debian
* Ubuntu sponsorship or sync review where applicable
